data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom updated, 2017 built  move in ready house in an adorable gated community.  Enjoy the breath taking views of nature from your private back yard while sitting under the covered patio. Putting green, outdoor TV, everything you need for entertaining!  Kitchen has high end stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, custom back splash and large walk in pantry. Upgraded tile floor throughout downstairs.  Downstairs also features a bedroom with 10 light French doors and a large walk in closet.  A half bath and dedicated laundry room with floor to ceiling storage shelves complete this homes perfection. Upstairs you will find the large primary suite with unobstructed nature views.  Soak in the tub in this stylish bathroom.  Dual sinks, separate shower, and large walk in closet.  Upstairs are two additional bedrooms and a full bath with separate sink and tub/shower area. The Westridge community of Canyon Hills has many amenities including such as basketball courts, outdoor BBQ and picnic areas, pool, jacuzzi, playground, dog park, and a back entrance to Starbucks!
